title: 'Crap': Stephen Colbert blasts CBS for denying it blocked James Talarico interview from air
summary_full: "Late Show" host Stephen Colbert has said CBS feared running afoul of the FCC if it broadcast a talk with the U.S. Senate candidate James Talarico.
summary_public: "Late Show" host Stephen Colbert has said CBS feared running afoul of the FCC if it broadcast a talk with the U.S. Senate candidate James Talarico.
